Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天的推理真是讓人大吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}超越常識的時間差詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.20,0:00:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}用滑雪手法製造的不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}看上去是小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}神秘溫泉雪夜振袖事件（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}明日香小姐進入露天溫泉是在10點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}繪麻小姐去庭院裏的祠堂是在10點半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.20,0:02:14.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兩人都是被這把神刀殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}神刀是在露天溫泉浴池裏被發現的 就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.10,0:02:21.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}犯罪過程是先殺害了繪麻小姐然後是明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.10,0:02:25.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}另外 在祠堂所在的庭院裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}只有繪麻小姐的足跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.40,0:02:32.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}而且在通往露天溫泉時必須通過的娛樂場裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}10點半以後始終有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}哪一個都是密室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}是參拜振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}櫻子小姐用參拜振袖的方法向兩人復仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}櫻子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}那是哪一位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我大學時的前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}被她們倆誣陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}承擔了秘密進行違禁藥品交易的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}因此自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}她們是指被殺害的明日香小姐和繪麻小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}所以 所以被前輩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真先警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}祠堂裏 遺體上戴的一隻耳環不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是留下的另一隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}啊 那個 是名牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概那樣的一隻也要20萬日元左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一對就要40萬日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}雖然不便宜 但也不至於成為殺人的理由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 春美小姐好像也有相同款式的項墜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}繪麻小姐好像很不高興看到我戴有同樣的項墜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}所以我立刻就摘掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}還有 在繪麻小姐的上衣口袋裏發現了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}另外 現場遺留的振袖和腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}是收藏在這個旅館儲藏室裏的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}一般沒有上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}所以任何人都可以拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}大概是兇手提前藏在現場的某處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼 來確認一下昨晚各位的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}首先是惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}你在9點半左右去了露天溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}10點左右出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}然後明日香小姐進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}是的 那以後我就回自己的房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}途中遇到毛利先生他們 大家站著聊了幾句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.30,0:04:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 當時我想邀請惠裏小姐去喝一杯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.30,0:04:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}賴子小姐從9點半開始就在這裏做採訪內容的整理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是的 我看到惠理小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:40.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}然後5分鐘後 我看到繪麻小姐到後門去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是10點半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.10,0:04:46.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}還有其他人去後門嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒有了 誰也沒去過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那時 毛利先生他們四個人去了露天溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是 女溫泉門口掛著“租出”的牌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且門也被鎖上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}於是你們兩位又回到了娛樂場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}毛利先生 入浴中發現什麼奇怪的事情了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.50,0:05:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}我們聽見女溫泉那邊有“嘩啦嘩啦”的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是什麼時候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}應該是10點50分左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}那不是犯案時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.20,0:05:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}但是只有“嘩啦嘩啦”的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}並沒有聽到慘叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:26.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}在她發出慘叫前就已被兇手用電擊槍擊暈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.20,0:05:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}當然是這樣沒錯的 小鬼不要妨礙調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蘭小姐和春美小姐一直呆在娛樂場嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是的 我忘了摘隱形眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}回房間了一趟 大概10分鐘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.40,0:05:58.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}那時候誰也沒有通過娛樂場 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.10,0:05:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}毛利先生從男溫泉出來是11點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.60,0:06:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}那時惠理小姐和賴子小姐在這裏商談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 阪東先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}11點15分左右開始和她們在一起商談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後毛利先生他們在露天溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}發現了明日香小姐的遺體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}關於振袖般若的紙人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}最初去的時候沒有掉在地上嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}接著在祠堂發現了繪麻小姐的遺體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}繪麻小姐為什麼會去祠堂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個問題提得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}理由是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.90,0:06:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}繪麻小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}有件事想和你秘密地談一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}今晚10點半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}在院裏的祠堂等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}阪東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}不 不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我沒寫過這樣的紙條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你在11點15分之前沒有不在場證明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.30,0:06:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是 我沒有殺她們兩人的動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}現在有動機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}好像只有春美小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}怎麼會 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.60,0:07:08.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}你因為那位自殺的前輩而對她倆心懷怨恨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}另外 在回房摘掉隱形眼鏡的這段時間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你並沒有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我 我沒做過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不論誰是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}不解開密室之謎的話也拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果兩人是被不同的兇器所殺害的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還好辦一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}還有 兇手為什麼要把現場模仿成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}如振袖般若的傳說那樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}送來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}終於送來了 驗屍報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}殺害兩人的兇器都是那把神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}如果兇器不同的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}這個問題還好辦一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}頭巾上只有繪麻小姐的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有現場和神社祠堂等地方的人偶身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以及繪麻小姐所持的紙條上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}均沒有查出指紋之類的與兇手有關的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那麼 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}真的很麻煩了呢 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼都沒發現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}接下來是昨天舉行的兒童雪橇大賽的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}好像很開心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:34.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}孩子們啊 電視裏的孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以足跡才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}漸漸搞清楚了 事情的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這邊積雪有15釐米左右啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}頂多能夠陷下去5釐米左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}15釐米和5釐米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}但是 為什麼那個人要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南 你去哪兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}稍微在周圍散散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}東京一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}阪東先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}等等 難道說那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.50,0:09:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 襪子全濕透了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快去把它烤幹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}小蘭姐姐 等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兇手是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}一定是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}但是 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果那個人是兇手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}又是什麼時候 怎麼把紙人偶放到這裏來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}剛才沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}就是覺得拿在手裏冷冷的 心裏發毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}高木嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}是我 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.40,0:10:51.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}其實是有點事想請你調查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}毛利叔叔說有點事想拜託您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果我的推理是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那個人就一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}你讓大家到這裏集合 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這還用說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}當然是揭開這個案件的真相了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}您知道兇手是誰了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}到底是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}按順序來說明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}從繪麻小姐被殺的振袖之神的祠堂密室之謎說起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真先警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}能請你把放在浴盆上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}數碼相機的電源開關打開好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.30,0:11:47.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我總覺得這個腳印有點不大對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我明白過來是在今天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個哪里不對勁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}是腳印太淺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨天白天 我到祠堂去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}腳陷入雪中大約7-8釐米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為之後也一直在下雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:13.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}晚上10點半左右到祠堂去的繪麻小姐的靴子鞋印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至少也應該有15釐米深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 實際上最多只有7-8釐米深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這也太淺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}原來如此 那是為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是因為腳印被壓平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}腳印被壓平了 被壓過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.30,0:12:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我為了不讓繪麻小姐的腳印被雪覆蓋掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在從後門延伸到祠堂的腳印之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蓋上了浴巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}如果這並非是浴巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}而是木板的話又會怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}從上邊走過的兇手 就能不留下腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.70,0:12:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而往返於後門與祠堂之間了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼簡單嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}掩人耳目的詭計有時就是這麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}恐怕 兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}準備了兩塊一米左右的木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}交替蓋在繪麻小姐的腳印上走過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.20,0:13:15.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}殺害了繪麻小姐後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}再用同樣的方法回到了後門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣一來 腳印雖然會稍微變淺一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但卻被保留了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}可是 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}兇手是怎樣進出後門的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 當時並沒有人經過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兇手是從屋簷下走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}用了同樣的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}所以才沒有人看到 也沒有留下腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}根據今天早上我所調查到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從後門出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}右邊的積雪上會留下15釐米深的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}左邊留下的卻只有5釐米深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}也就是說 兇手是從左邊過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}順著長廊的屋簷走下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}到了某個地方積雪又開始變厚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那…那麼 那是哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}就是你的房間前面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}明智惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}惠理老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}惠理小姐在明日香小姐入浴之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}離開了露天溫泉 回到了自己的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用剛才的方法 從後門走到祠堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:34.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把事先以阪東先生的名義叫出來的繪麻小姐給殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的確 用那種方法我是能殺了繪麻小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 要殺明日香小姐卻是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}的確 建在峭壁半山腰的這座露天溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用同樣的方法是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}可是當時並沒有人經過娛樂場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.80,0:14:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:14:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}明日香小姐是在繪麻小姐之前被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.60,0:15:06.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理小姐用電擊槍將明日香小姐擊暈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後脫掉明日香小姐的衣物後把她殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}接著把屍體裹上預先藏好的腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}一起扔進了溫泉浴池裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}恐怕 神刀是在前一天的晚上事先偷走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.00,0:15:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}如果繪麻小姐是在明日香小姐之後被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.00,0:15:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}神刀和沾血的頭巾又為什麼會在溫泉這裏被發現的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}那個紙人偶也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}那是用乾冰製造的機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}利用小塊乾冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把人偶固定在天花板的縫隙裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果事先計算過乾冰揮發所需要時間的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.60,0:15:45.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}就可以在任何時候 讓人偶落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以人偶才是冰涼冰涼的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.60,0:15:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理小姐拜託老闆每天都給她買蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是為了弄到乾冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}紙人偶倒是這樣就可以解釋清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是神刀和頭巾又怎麼解釋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我在10點半之後可沒去過女溫泉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}不到這裏來 也可以讓它們出現在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}現在就來實際演練一遍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.00,0:16:35.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}這木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}是從峭壁之上的惠理小姐的房間滑下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請大家想像一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}用來殺害繪麻小姐的神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沾有繪麻小姐血跡的頭巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}用這個方法的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}就算不出房間也能讓它們出現在女溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}毛利先生你們在入浴的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}聽到的“嘩啦嘩啦”的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}就是木板滑下來掉到水中的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}惠理小姐就是用了這個手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}讓我們對行兇的順序產生錯誤的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}從而讓她的不在場證明得以成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}那兩塊關鍵的木板又到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 我拿來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.00,0:17:23.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是儲藏室裏其他的腰帶 我把它們給凍得硬梆梆的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用水把腰帶浸濕後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}放在室外一個晚上的時間就會被凍成像冰塊一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她就是利用了被冰凍的腰帶來代替了這兩塊木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是嗎 既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}掉進溫泉裏的話 腰帶就會恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:45.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}浴池裏的遺體旁漂浮著兩條腰帶會被人懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此 她就在浴池裏放了很多條腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在祠堂裏也鋪上了很多件振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}模仿振袖般若的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.40,0:17:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}就是為了隱藏這個手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是精彩之極的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}可你有什麼證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請你讓大家看看你的腳底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請你務必讓大家看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}抱歉了 惠理老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像是因為踩到了什麼尖的東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}不 這就是你殺害繪麻小姐的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}踩到了她掉落的耳環而留下的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨晚 在進行現場保護的那段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}我讓大家聚集在客廳裏等候的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為惠理小姐說讓大家坐下來比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}就改到大廳去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.20,0:18:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}當時你右腳上的傷口還流著血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:58.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以你才不願意去必須脫掉拖鞋的客廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你有什麼證據證明這個傷口是那只耳環所傷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不見了的那只耳環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}被我給找到了 看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}一隻就值20萬日元的名牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.90,0:19:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}只要在這上面檢驗出有她的血跡 就是證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}竟然 被你給找到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實這是 找春美小姐借的項鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我殺了她們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為什麼 要做這樣毫無意義的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}不是惠理 是智惠理老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你隱瞞了你的真名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.60,0:20:02.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為“明”這個姓實在是太少見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.20,0:20:05.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}所以大家都把“明 智惠理”誤當成“明智 惠理”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.70,0:20:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我讓警視廳的熟人調查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.90,0:20:10.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}智惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.50,0:20:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}你就是那位自殺了的鈴鹿櫻子小姐的親姐姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理老師是櫻子小姐的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}自幼因為火災失去了父母的你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.30,0:20:28.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只有妹妹櫻子小姐被鈴鹿家收養了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我會說出一切的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}妹妹自殺的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}我在波士頓學習寫小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}被告知她的死訊 是一年之後的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柔弱的櫻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}居然因為被懷疑和違禁藥物的販賣有關就自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我真是既後悔 又憐惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為什麼一點都不和我商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是她姐姐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.10,0:21:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}她是我唯一的親人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我無法饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}櫻子太悲慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.60,0:21:09.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}然後 以這次的工作為由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:14.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我假裝若無其事找到大學同班的賴子小姐叫來了那兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.70,0:21:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以模仿振袖般若的復仇傳說向她們復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣 櫻子小姐就會開心了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這次採訪的三個人裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}唯一一個對櫻子小姐信賴理解的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}深津春美小姐如果沒來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.70,0:21:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我就不會知道你妹妹自殺的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就不會懷疑到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}櫻子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.00,0:21:50.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}簡直就像為了勸解想要犯罪的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.80,0:21:55.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}讓春美小姐和你 相遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}春美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}如同被般若附身的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}完全沒有感受到櫻子小姐的心意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我怎麼會在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.30,0:23:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不妙的兆頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.20,0:23:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}糟了
